ngZeroOut.\n\nThis is NOT the same as a traditional\nnegative prompt.\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------\n\nStep 3 - Sampling / Image Generation\n\nUses:\n• Dual Model CFG Guider\n• Ideogram 4 Scheduler\n• SamplerCustomAdvanced\n\nThis differs from the standard KSampler pipeline.\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------\n\nMy Test Setup (Very Low VRAM)\n\nTested with:\n\nComfyUI 0.27.0\n\nRTX 2080 8 GB\nSystem RAM 64 GB\n\nModels\n\n• ideogram4_fp8_scaled\n• ideogram4_ideogram4Fp8Uncond\n• flux2-vae\n• Qwen3VL-8B-Uncensored-HauhauCS GGUF  (CLIP Type = ideogram4)\n\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":30,"type":"Note","pos":[3538.3244918262335,351.10217130817614],"size":[414,620],"flags":{},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Important Notes","properties":{},"widgets_values":["**** IMPORTANT ******\n\nThis workflow uses:\n\nCLIPLoader (GGUF)\nType = ideogram4\n\nDo NOT use:\n\n• DualCLIPLoader\n• Type = flux\n\nThose will cause CLIP loading errors.\n\n------------------------------------------------------\n\nThis workflow intentionally contains only the\ncore Ideogram 4 inference pipeline.\n\nIt is designed as a learning/reference workflow.\n\nOnce verified, it can be extended with:\n\n• LoRAs\n• Prompt Builder\n• Image-to-Image\n• Upscalers\n• ControlNet\n\n------------------------------------------------------\n\n\nCredits\n\n• Ideogram AI for the model architecture\n• Original workflow author(s) whose workflow\n  served as the implementation reference\n• This workflow focuses on simplifying and\n  documenting the core inference pipeline\n  for educational purposes."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":31,"type":"Note","pos":[3219.3244918262335,353.10217130817614],"size":[312,618],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Workflow Notes","properties":{},"widgets_values":["Version 1.0\n\nCreated from scratch after studying\nthe official Ideogram4 workflow.\n\nPurpose\n\n✓ Educational\n✓ Minimal\n✓ Easy to extend\n\nVerified\n\n✓ Text-to-Image\n\nNext\n\n□ Prompt Builder\n□ LoRA\n□ Image-to-Image\n□ ControlNet"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"}],"links":[[8,10,0,7,0,"CONDITIONING"],[9,10,0,11,1,"CONDITIONING"],[10,7,0,11,3,"CONDITIONING"],[13,1,0,11,0,"MODEL"],[14,2,0,11,2,"MODEL"],[17,15,0,18,0,"NOISE"],[18,16,0,18,4,"LATENT"],[19,17,0,18,3,"SIGMAS"],[20,11,0,18,1,"GUIDER"],[23,21,0,22,0,"IMAGE"],[24,20,0,21,0,"IMAGE"],[25,18,0,20,0,"LATENT"],[26,23,0,18,2,"SAMPLER"],[29,24,0,19,0,"CLIP"],[30,4,0,19,1,"VAE"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"Ideogram - Model Loading","bounding":[4550.824491826234,322.10217130817614,433,640],"color":"#3f789e","flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"Prompt Guidance","bounding":[5016.824491826234,323.10217130817614,420,537],"color":"#b58b2a","flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"Image Generation Process","bounding":[5471.824491826234,324.10217130817614,539.1916687011717,537],"color":"#8A8","flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"ue_links":[{"downstream":10,"downstream_slot":0,"upstream":"24","upstream_slot":0,"controller":19,"type":"CLIP"},{"downstream":20,"downstream_slot":1,"upstream":"4","upstream_slot":0,"controller":19,"type":"VAE"}],"ds":{"scale":1,"offset":[-3140.3244918262335,-217.10217130817614]},"links_added_by_ue":[31,32]},"version":0.4}